72% of those interviewed had nothing good to say about the liberalization of divorce in the country. They argued that most people are insensitive towards the threats of divorce and this has led to many bad marriages. This has affected the reputation of the country as a whole, and many outsiders will avoid marrying into this country.

Why you should promote Cultural Understandings

Understanding beliefs of all types and learning how to live with them, work with them and entertain them is termed as cultural understanding. Compared to most countries in the world, San Marino adopts all kinds of beliefs and values extremely fast. This country is open to innovations and more businesses in developed countries are flocking this country. Some of these businesses and ideas would hardly be adopted in other countries, but this small nation embraces everything that has the potential to make them great.

The westernization of life in San Marino is another thing that will make it great, with the ancient environment withering away at a very fast rate. The true old way of living will be misplaced before long. Today’s beliefs and philosophies are the strands of the ancient cultural fabrics being overlooked and slowly washed away with new innovations. The rich fabrics will now be reduced to important museums, history books or LED screens.
